data.description: Check out this One Story Beauty, move in ready and at this price in Deer Park. This may just be what you have been looking for. So many updates, including Flooring, Kitchen Counters and Back Splash, Fixtures, Bathrooms and an amazing covered patio that will allow you the perfect space to unwind after a long day, entertain or the kiddo's 2 or 4 legged to play. Split floor plan, high ceilings are 2 things you will notice as you enter through the front door. The beautiful serene feeling gives you the perfect place to relax at when you are at home. Walk to elementary or Dow Park. Large storage shed in back yard gives you a place to store items yet free up your garage space. Close to freeways, shopping and more. Call any Realtor today for more information or to schedule a showing before its gone.
